1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,229
[I Don't Want To Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:48,620
Eun Suh is so pitiful!

4
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,820
She is not only tortured by leukemia,

5
00:01:52,820 --> 00:01:56,970
but also abandoned by Joon Suh because
he wants to return to America with Yoo Mi.

6
00:01:58,810 --> 00:02:00,920
She obviously had ample opportunity to be
in a relationship with the male lead,

7
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:03,650
but she always consumed the affection
of the supporting male.

8
00:02:04,070 --> 00:02:07,010
Isn't she eliciting others' sympathy
with her tears and innocence?

9
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:08,990
She is a fake softie.

10
00:02:08,990 --> 00:02:10,539
What does it mean?

11
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:14,280
That means she pretends to be a weak girl

12
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,370
to win the heart of the prince.

13
00:02:15,830 --> 00:02:17,720
It's especially used to fool
ignorant girls like you.

14
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:19,910
You are the ignorant one.

15
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:22,130
We are willing to be a fool
because of love.

16
00:02:22,130 --> 00:02:23,310
You are sober right now.

17
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:24,360
But when you are in love,

18
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,530
we are all the same.

19
00:02:25,530 --> 00:02:26,120
I agree.

20
00:02:26,460 --> 00:02:27,960
I won't.

21
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:30,030
I want to have a freer
and more independent life.

22
00:02:30,030 --> 00:02:31,290
I won't be ignorant even if I am in love.

23
00:02:31,290 --> 00:02:32,300
I am not a fool.

24
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,970
Do you think

25
00:02:38,420 --> 00:02:40,650
falling in love will make people foolish?

26
00:02:41,490 --> 00:02:42,380
I don't think so.

27
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:44,010
I don't think I'm getting foolish.

28
00:02:45,990 --> 00:02:47,210
Definitely not.

29
00:02:47,210 --> 00:02:49,260
You've been foolish since I first met you.

30
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,620
That's probably because

31
00:02:51,620 --> 00:02:53,040
when you first met me,

32
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:54,350
I have already fallen in love.

33
00:02:55,820 --> 00:02:57,829
Where did you learn these?

34
00:02:57,829 --> 00:02:59,010
They are from my heart.

35
00:03:00,310 --> 00:03:01,360
Enough. Watch the film.

36
00:03:04,260 --> 00:03:10,430
[Episode 20: Only Be A Fool For Love]

37
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:26,260
Li Qing Tong.

38
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,500
No matter what I say,

39
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:33,820
I hope you can listen to me
with patience, okay?

40
00:03:37,810 --> 00:03:39,370
What are you going to say?

41
00:03:39,370 --> 00:03:41,010
You make me nervous.

42
00:03:42,010 --> 00:03:43,060
Do you know

43
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,450
how my exam was?

44
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:46,300
You did well, didn't you?

45
00:03:48,390 --> 00:03:49,990
If all goes well,

46
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:53,520
I can go to my ideal university.

47
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,500
Is that true?

48
00:03:58,860 --> 00:04:00,490
Awesome!

49
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:03,060
This is because of you.

50
00:04:04,110 --> 00:04:05,370
Because you changed me.

51
00:04:07,340 --> 00:04:08,680
Your slap

52
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:11,040
made me realise that

53
00:04:13,510 --> 00:04:15,870
I can accept myself to be
a good-for-nothing bum,

54
00:04:17,670 --> 00:04:18,470
but

55
00:04:19,269 --> 00:04:20,360
I can't accept that

56
00:04:20,779 --> 00:04:22,079
you see me as a good-for-nothing bum.

57
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,159
Li Qing Tong,

58
00:04:34,850 --> 00:04:36,110
I like you very much.

59
00:04:36,740 --> 00:04:38,970
I have liked you for a long time.

60
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,120
But I dare not admit it.

61
00:04:45,930 --> 00:04:47,740
Because I am not good enough.

62
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:51,310
I treat you,

63
00:04:52,110 --> 00:04:53,080
everyone,

64
00:04:53,740 --> 00:04:55,720
and even myself terribly.

65
00:04:57,950 --> 00:04:59,970
But I really don't want to
have any regrets.

66
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,080
After graduation,

67
00:05:05,010 --> 00:05:06,640
we almost lost contact with each other.

68
00:05:07,860 --> 00:05:10,170
I can't accept that anymore.

69
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:13,070
Therefore,

70
00:05:13,490 --> 00:05:15,170
I must speak out.

71
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:21,130
Are you willing to be my girlfriend

72
00:05:21,890 --> 00:05:23,610
and be with me?

73
00:05:33,130 --> 00:05:33,940
I'm sorry.

74
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,550
I know this is out of the blue.

75
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:44,480
Do I have to reply now?

76
00:05:46,159 --> 00:05:47,170
Of course not.

77
00:05:47,970 --> 00:05:48,970
I also hope

78
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:50,570
you can think about it carefully.

79
00:05:50,570 --> 00:05:53,040
I don't need to think about it.
Of course I'm willing to.

80
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:04,810
Why are you smiling?

81
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:10,270
Are you kidding me?

82
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,490
Thank you.

83
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,560
I'm the one who should thank you.

84
00:06:36,350 --> 00:06:37,990
If you didn't say anything,

85
00:06:37,990 --> 00:06:40,390
I'm afraid I can't help but confess first.

86
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:41,690
That will be embarrassing.

87
00:06:52,780 --> 00:06:54,250
Why are you still smiling?

88
00:08:01,910 --> 00:08:04,930
We have learned many ancient articles.

89
00:08:04,930 --> 00:08:07,740
We know that since ancient times,

90
00:08:07,740 --> 00:08:11,440
language, phonetics,
vocabulary and grammar

91
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,150
are constantly developing.

92
00:08:12,150 --> 00:08:13,200
What's the matter with you?

93
00:08:15,220 --> 00:08:17,190
I'm thinking about the most
important event of my life.

94
00:08:17,190 --> 00:08:17,990
What's that?

95
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:21,980
You won't understand even if I tell you.

96
00:08:27,180 --> 00:08:29,420
Are you sure you are going to
the kindergarten with me?

97
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:30,800
Why do you ask?

98
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,770
I can't go?

99
00:08:32,309 --> 00:08:33,230
No, that's not what I mean.

100
00:08:33,909 --> 00:08:35,539
I'm afraid that you

101
00:08:35,539 --> 00:08:37,190
can't stand those kids.

102
00:08:38,659 --> 00:08:39,450
Listen.

103
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,890
There's nothing I can't stand right now.

104
00:08:41,890 --> 00:08:43,320
I only can't stand this place.

105
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:53,610
What's wrong?

106
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,350
Where's Chen Jun He?

107
00:08:57,350 --> 00:09:00,410
He has gone for a practice in early
childhood education with Jiang Da Fan.

108
00:09:00,410 --> 00:09:01,380
Who's Jiang Da Fan?

109
00:09:01,380 --> 00:09:02,220
Male or female?

110
00:09:02,220 --> 00:09:03,440
His roommate.

111
00:09:03,980 --> 00:09:04,990
You forgot him?

112
00:09:04,990 --> 00:09:06,240
You met him before.

113
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:07,380
Right.

114
00:09:08,180 --> 00:09:09,320
What's the matter with you?

115
00:09:10,030 --> 00:09:11,500
You seem very worried.

116
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:12,720
Are you worried about something?

117
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:15,360
No.

118
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:17,000
I'm just anxious.

119
00:09:17,460 --> 00:09:19,480
Li Qing Tong is in a relationship now.

120
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,750
Shouldn't Chen Jun He feel threatened?

121
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:22,380
He...

122
00:09:22,380 --> 00:09:23,760
Isn't he anxious?

123
00:09:24,170 --> 00:09:25,570
Li Qing Tong is not his wife.

124
00:09:25,570 --> 00:09:26,660
Why should he be anxious?

125
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:28,590
Well, Li Qing Tong is his wife.

126
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,080
Will she become his wife
just because you think so?

127
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:36,320
What you say doesn't count.

128
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:38,080
You won't understand even if I tell you.

129
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:40,560
Forget it.

130
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:41,700
Just eat.

131
00:10:04,170 --> 00:10:08,030
Who comes to a library
for their first date?

132
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:11,220
When you first pretended to bump into me,

133
00:10:11,220 --> 00:10:12,650
wasn't it in the library too?

134
00:10:13,990 --> 00:10:15,510
You still remember that?

135
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:21,260
You ignored me all day that day,

136
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:22,440
and looked fierce too.

137
00:10:23,110 --> 00:10:23,740
Wait.

138
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:26,590
Did you secretly pay attention
to me since that day?

139
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,760
Are you hungry?

140
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,810
You didn't answer me.

141
00:10:32,810 --> 00:10:34,910
Don't divert the topic
by asking me if I'm hungry.

142
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:35,910
I'm hungry.

143
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:36,510
Come with me.

144
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:37,640
Let's have some Japanese food.

145
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:54,860
Where are you going?

146
00:11:01,450 --> 00:11:02,080
Sorry.

147
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,550
We just quarrelled.

148
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:05,150
I'm going to go now. Don't mind her.

149
00:11:08,930 --> 00:11:10,190
[Lin Yang Teachers College]

150
00:11:10,820 --> 00:11:14,220
She's just being herself. Don't mind her.

151
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:24,170
What's wrong?

152
00:11:24,170 --> 00:11:25,180
You don't like the food?

153
00:11:26,110 --> 00:11:27,400
They are raw,

154
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:28,670
and not delicious.

155
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:30,980
Let's eat northeast vermicelli
in the future.

156
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:34,460
By the way,

157
00:11:35,010 --> 00:11:36,970
you haven't received your
admission notice yet, have you?

158
00:11:37,740 --> 00:11:38,540
Yes.

159
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:40,260
Will there be a problem?

160
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:41,350
Don't worry.

161
00:11:41,350 --> 00:11:42,110
It's going to be fine.

162
00:11:43,070 --> 00:11:43,960
It's just that

163
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:45,510
I am a little anxious.

164
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:46,180
Why?

165
00:11:46,690 --> 00:11:48,030
In a top university,

166
00:11:48,490 --> 00:11:50,500
everyone is the best elite

167
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,930
from all over the country.

168
00:11:51,930 --> 00:11:54,540
Kids like me, who come from a small place,

169
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,600
are only top of the class here.

170
00:11:57,140 --> 00:11:59,790
I will become the tail of a lion
from the head of a dog when I get there.

171
00:12:00,070 --> 00:12:02,350
I'm afraid that I can't adapt to the gap.

172
00:12:04,370 --> 00:12:05,670
There's nothing to be afraid of.

173
00:12:05,670 --> 00:12:07,140
The tail of a lion is also
a part of a lion.

174
00:12:07,140 --> 00:12:08,950
It's still better than
the tail of a dog like me.

175
00:12:09,450 --> 00:12:10,790
You are a girl.

176
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:12,840
Do not compare yourself to a dog.

177
00:12:18,310 --> 00:12:19,950
Why did you make such a joke?

178
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:22,050
I only do it occasionally.

179
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:23,900
I'll go back now.

180
00:12:24,860 --> 00:12:25,450
Bye.

181
00:12:27,470 --> 00:12:28,900
I'll see you tomorrow.

182
00:12:28,900 --> 00:12:30,110
Have a good rest.

183
00:12:40,490 --> 00:12:41,160
Stop looking.

184
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:42,210
That's enough.

185
00:12:43,050 --> 00:12:44,140
Why are you here?

186
00:12:44,140 --> 00:12:45,070
I'm waiting for you.

187
00:12:45,490 --> 00:12:46,540
Waiting for me?

188
00:12:49,730 --> 00:12:50,900
After you go back,

189
00:12:50,900 --> 00:12:52,110
have a talk with Hua.

190
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:53,970
I'm a little worried about her.

191
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:56,910
What's the matter with her?

192
00:12:58,830 --> 00:12:59,810
How should I say this?

193
00:13:01,610 --> 00:13:02,500
She is

194
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,230
probably dissatisfied

195
00:13:06,490 --> 00:13:07,450
with Wu Zhi Xun.

196
00:13:09,380 --> 00:13:10,850
She was previously dissatisfied
with Chen Jun He.

197
00:13:10,850 --> 00:13:12,660
Now she is dissatisfied with Wu Zhi Xun?

198
00:13:12,870 --> 00:13:13,370
Well,

199
00:13:13,370 --> 00:13:14,890
who should I be with
that will make her happy?

200
00:13:14,890 --> 00:13:15,880
Should I be with you?

201
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:17,200
No, no, no. It's not suitable.

202
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,620
I don't think it's suitable too.

203
00:13:19,620 --> 00:13:20,890
Appalling!

204
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:23,120
Go back and talk to her.

205
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,040
I know.

206
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:25,090
Don't quarrel.

207
00:13:25,090 --> 00:13:25,970
I know.

208
00:13:25,970 --> 00:13:26,850
Take it seriously.

209
00:13:26,850 --> 00:13:27,740
I know.

210
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,110
Hua.

211
00:13:33,870 --> 00:13:35,420
Please come out. I want to talk to you.

212
00:13:43,910 --> 00:13:44,790
What's the matter with them?

213
00:13:46,430 --> 00:13:47,730
In my experience,

214
00:13:48,530 --> 00:13:50,120
I'm afraid it's because of men.

215
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:53,270
Hua,

216
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:55,710
we always talk about everything
with each other.

217
00:13:56,170 --> 00:13:57,300
So tell me honestly.

218
00:13:57,640 --> 00:14:00,030
Are you unhappy because I'm
in a relationship with Wu Zhi Xun?

219
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:01,630
Yes.

220
00:14:02,050 --> 00:14:03,600
Well, why are you unhappy?

221
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:17,670
You are really strange.

222
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:19,520
You are always so capricious.

223
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:21,030
You insisted at that time that

224
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:22,330
Chen Jun He is a jerk.

225
00:14:22,330 --> 00:14:23,640
I must never get close to him.

226
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:25,910
Now you do everything to get us together.

227
00:14:25,910 --> 00:14:27,080
You did the same with Wu Zhi Xun.

228
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,220
At that time, didn't you

229
00:14:28,220 --> 00:14:30,270
rack your brain to push him towards me?

230
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:32,630
Now we are finally in a relationship.

231
00:14:32,630 --> 00:14:33,260
But you are unhappy

232
00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:34,260
and unwilling again.

233
00:14:34,260 --> 00:14:35,610
What on earth do you want?

234
00:14:35,610 --> 00:14:37,460
What on earth do you want me to do?

235
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:40,050
Do I have to fill in an application to you
before I do anything?

236
00:14:40,050 --> 00:14:41,610
Or why don't you just
draw up a schedule for me?

237
00:14:41,610 --> 00:14:43,340
I will just listen to you every day.

238
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:46,100
Well, I...

239
00:14:46,610 --> 00:14:48,000
I did nothing.

240
00:14:48,380 --> 00:14:50,600
Why are you so angry suddenly?

241
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:52,320
I'm just not happy with myself, okay?

242
00:14:54,420 --> 00:14:56,940
Well then, why are you unhappy?

243
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,590
It's you who told me

244
00:14:59,590 --> 00:15:01,230
to follow my heart

245
00:15:01,230 --> 00:15:02,490
and enjoy the process.

246
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:04,210
I've listened to you.

247
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:07,400
Now I'm following my heart.

248
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:08,830
What's wrong with that now?

249
00:15:08,830 --> 00:15:10,260
Of course there's a problem.

250
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:11,510
What's the problem?

251
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:17,690
Look, you don't even have a reason.

252
00:15:17,690 --> 00:15:18,910
You only want to control
other people's relationship.

253
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:20,000
You are really a bully!

254
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,430
I have a reason.

255
00:15:21,430 --> 00:15:22,820
The reason is that Wu Zhi Xun
treats you badly.

256
00:15:22,820 --> 00:15:23,570
When did he do that?

257
00:15:23,570 --> 00:15:24,330
He...

258
00:15:28,860 --> 00:15:30,370
Look, you just want to control others.

259
00:15:30,370 --> 00:15:31,340
You control me more than anyone.

260
00:15:31,340 --> 00:15:32,560
You control me more than my mom.

261
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:33,520
If I had a daughter like you,

262
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:35,200
I would have been absolutely furious.

263
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:39,780
Li Qing Tong, you push me
because of a guy?

264
00:15:39,780 --> 00:15:40,780
You have no conscience.

265
00:15:40,780 --> 00:15:41,380
I...

266
00:15:41,590 --> 00:15:42,970
I won't talk to you anymore.

267
00:15:54,060 --> 00:15:55,320
What's the matter with them?

268
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:56,620
Don't ask.

269
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:57,590
You might be scolded.

270
00:16:02,430 --> 00:16:06,220
[Outstanding Dormitory Competition,
Dorm 201, Best Roommate Award]

271
00:16:36,730 --> 00:16:37,440
How did it go?

272
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:39,130
No talking with her.

273
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:42,940
What's this now?

274
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,610
What happened?

275
00:16:53,610 --> 00:16:54,790
You fell out with each other.

276
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:55,760
Where's your master?

277
00:16:55,760 --> 00:16:56,940
She's eating noodles on the second floor.

278
00:16:57,270 --> 00:16:58,530
She said nothing when I ask her.

279
00:16:58,830 --> 00:17:00,510
I have to make an excuse
to get out and come ask you.

280
00:17:00,510 --> 00:17:01,510
Ask me what?

281
00:17:01,510 --> 00:17:02,940
I don't care about her.

282
00:17:02,940 --> 00:17:04,369
It's no big deal.

283
00:17:04,369 --> 00:17:05,079
You don't have to go that far.

284
00:17:05,589 --> 00:17:08,490
I just can't get over that fact that
she tries to control me in everything.

285
00:17:08,490 --> 00:17:10,109
She did that for your own good.

286
00:17:10,630 --> 00:17:13,060
You only think you can't
go to university without Wu Zhi Xun.

287
00:17:13,060 --> 00:17:14,619
But without Hua, you can't
go to university as well.

288
00:17:15,329 --> 00:17:16,050
And think about it.

289
00:17:16,420 --> 00:17:17,680
When you were in trouble,

290
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:19,910
she was also anxious and
kept thinking of solutions.

291
00:17:19,910 --> 00:17:21,089
She got so high a score,

292
00:17:21,089 --> 00:17:22,430
but she chose to go to
the same university with you.

293
00:17:22,770 --> 00:17:24,990
This is a true sense of loyalty.

294
00:17:26,210 --> 00:17:27,849
When you told her that Wu Zhi Xun
drove you out that day,

295
00:17:28,310 --> 00:17:30,320
do you know how mad she was about it?

296
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:34,190
She's afraid that you will continue
to suffer if you are with Wu Zhi Xun.

297
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:35,530
Well.

298
00:17:35,990 --> 00:17:36,920
The key is that

299
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:39,020
I don't think Wu Zhi Xun treats me badly.

300
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:41,290
We are happy when we are together.

301
00:17:41,830 --> 00:17:42,590
So

302
00:17:43,010 --> 00:17:44,350
you must prove that.

303
00:17:45,570 --> 00:17:47,590
Although she is not qualified
to meddle in your business,

304
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,900
she is still your best friend.

305
00:17:50,320 --> 00:17:51,910
You should dispel her doubts,

306
00:17:51,910 --> 00:17:53,170
and not make her worry.

307
00:17:53,170 --> 00:17:54,810
That is the best solution.

308
00:17:55,520 --> 00:17:56,200
Well.

309
00:17:56,870 --> 00:17:58,040
How do I prove it?

310
00:17:58,040 --> 00:17:59,090
It's easy.

311
00:17:59,430 --> 00:18:00,980
Firstly, you should reduce your tensions,

312
00:18:00,980 --> 00:18:01,950
and then find time

313
00:18:01,950 --> 00:18:03,210
for the four of us to get together.

314
00:18:03,210 --> 00:18:05,270
Show us how good your relationship is.

315
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:06,400
She will not be anxious then.

316
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:11,230
Okay.

317
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:14,510
Xiao, you sometimes are smart.

318
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:15,350
I'm smarter than you.

319
00:18:15,350 --> 00:18:16,650
Hurry up. I'm going off now.

320
00:18:21,290 --> 00:18:24,020
[Classroom Building]

321
00:18:42,770 --> 00:18:43,700
Don't avoid me.

322
00:18:46,090 --> 00:18:47,770
Stop being angry.

323
00:18:48,280 --> 00:18:49,070
Listen.

324
00:18:49,070 --> 00:18:49,900
One who is always angry

325
00:18:49,900 --> 00:18:51,380
will grow ugly and old easily.

326
00:18:51,380 --> 00:18:52,010
After that...

327
00:18:52,390 --> 00:18:53,440
After that, Duan Xiao
will no longer love you.

328
00:18:55,330 --> 00:18:56,420
Then you apologize to me.

329
00:18:59,280 --> 00:19:01,460
Okay. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

330
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:03,940
I should not be so impulsive.

331
00:19:03,940 --> 00:19:06,380
I should not say things to you.

332
00:19:06,380 --> 00:19:08,690
I should not be so fierce.

333
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:12,260
I am not angry about what you said.

334
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:14,190
I am angry because you pushed me.

335
00:19:17,550 --> 00:19:19,440
Why didn't you push me back?

336
00:19:23,460 --> 00:19:24,980
You're so annoying.

337
00:19:27,420 --> 00:19:29,350
You pushed me too hard.

338
00:19:29,350 --> 00:19:30,860
Why are you pushing me again?

339
00:19:30,860 --> 00:19:31,200
You...

340
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:32,330
You deliberately take revenge on me.

341
00:19:32,330 --> 00:19:32,750
You push me again.

342
00:19:32,750 --> 00:19:33,510
You take revenge on me.

343
00:19:33,510 --> 00:19:34,350
We're equal now.

344
00:19:34,350 --> 00:19:35,230
Are you insane?

345
00:19:35,230 --> 00:19:35,990
You are so insane that...

346
00:19:35,990 --> 00:19:36,830
You are crazy.

347
00:19:36,830 --> 00:19:37,620
Go away.

348
00:19:37,620 --> 00:19:38,630
Don't push me.

349
00:19:43,340 --> 00:19:45,060
I have something to discuss with you.

350
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:47,790
After they arrive,

351
00:19:48,380 --> 00:19:50,180
can you listen to me?

352
00:19:50,390 --> 00:19:52,280
In other words, you do
whatever I want you to do.

353
00:19:52,870 --> 00:19:54,550
Just put up act with me.

354
00:19:54,890 --> 00:19:56,270
Why do I have to put up act?

355
00:19:56,900 --> 00:19:57,700
To show

356
00:19:57,700 --> 00:19:59,380
your thoughtfulness for me.

357
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:01,940
You need to make Hua feel that
we are in a good relationship

358
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:03,750
and you treat me very well.

359
00:20:03,750 --> 00:20:05,050
Then she will have nothing to say.

360
00:20:05,050 --> 00:20:06,230
I am in a relationship with you,

361
00:20:06,230 --> 00:20:07,650
not her.

362
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:09,960
That's not what I mean.

363
00:20:10,430 --> 00:20:12,530
Our relationship is our own business.

364
00:20:12,530 --> 00:20:14,000
Why do you need her approval?

365
00:20:16,380 --> 00:20:17,860
That's not what I mean too.

366
00:20:17,860 --> 00:20:19,080
I just think that

367
00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:21,000
you two are the most
important people in my life.

368
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:23,240
I hope you two can get along.

369
00:20:24,660 --> 00:20:25,420
Here you are.

370
00:20:33,190 --> 00:20:34,160
Let's catch some dolls.

371
00:20:41,630 --> 00:20:43,140
Okay. I get it.

372
00:20:43,310 --> 00:20:44,700
Are you angry?

373
00:20:45,030 --> 00:20:45,870
No.

374
00:20:46,080 --> 00:20:47,600
Let's go and play with them.

375
00:20:50,790 --> 00:20:51,540
Today,

376
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:52,930
I will show you

377
00:20:52,930 --> 00:20:55,030
what a perfect boyfriend means.

378
00:20:55,830 --> 00:20:56,320
Here.

379
00:20:56,540 --> 00:20:57,300
Choose one you like.

380
00:20:58,350 --> 00:20:59,060
This one.

381
00:20:59,820 --> 00:21:00,490
Okay.

382
00:21:00,490 --> 00:21:01,370
Within two minutes,

383
00:21:01,370 --> 00:21:02,510
I promise you that it will be yours.

384
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:16,030
I missed it.

385
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:17,580
It's okay. Let's do it again.

386
00:21:44,340 --> 00:21:45,930
How about we switch turns?

387
00:21:45,930 --> 00:21:48,580
There must be something wrong
with the machine.

388
00:21:48,580 --> 00:21:50,470
Is this a scam?

389
00:21:53,110 --> 00:21:55,510
You haven't caught anything?

390
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:01,180
What else do you want?

391
00:22:01,180 --> 00:22:02,060
I'll catch it for you.

392
00:22:04,030 --> 00:22:04,960
That one. That one.

393
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:05,500
I want that one.

394
00:22:05,500 --> 00:22:06,430
Okay. Let's go.

395
00:22:11,850 --> 00:22:12,850
You just wait.

396
00:22:12,850 --> 00:22:14,740
I won't go home until I catch one.

397
00:22:18,390 --> 00:22:20,880
There must be something wrong
with the machine.

398
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:23,770
It's okay.

399
00:22:23,770 --> 00:22:24,780
I am not demanding.

400
00:22:24,780 --> 00:22:25,660
One is enough.

401
00:22:29,180 --> 00:22:30,030
I want a drink.

402
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:32,040
Okay. What do you want?

403
00:22:34,350 --> 00:22:35,740
I don't want a drink now.

404
00:22:36,580 --> 00:22:37,470
I want juice.

405
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:38,470
I want juice

406
00:22:38,470 --> 00:22:39,610
that is freshly-squeezed

407
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,470
and has no water added.

408
00:22:42,470 --> 00:22:43,770
I want freshly-squeezed orange juice.

409
00:22:43,770 --> 00:22:44,530
Okay.

410
00:22:47,260 --> 00:22:48,360
Buy for them too.

411
00:22:50,360 --> 00:22:51,580
No, I don't want to drink anything.

412
00:22:54,410 --> 00:22:55,190
No way.

413
00:22:55,190 --> 00:22:56,660
You hardly drank anything all day.

414
00:22:56,660 --> 00:22:57,340
You must drink something.

415
00:22:57,340 --> 00:22:58,390
Buy one for her.

416
00:22:58,760 --> 00:22:59,810
I am not thirsty.

417
00:23:00,610 --> 00:23:01,760
It's fine. You go and buy the juice.

418
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:03,650
We will drink after you buy them back.

419
00:23:03,650 --> 00:23:04,690
I really won't drink.

420
00:23:06,380 --> 00:23:07,120
Li Jin Bu.

421
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:10,150
Are you against our relationship?

422
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,570
I don't care what you think.

423
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:18,460
This relationship is between
Li Qing Tong and me.

424
00:23:19,180 --> 00:23:20,440
It has nothing to do with you.

425
00:23:20,760 --> 00:23:22,940
But I want everyone to know that

426
00:23:22,940 --> 00:23:24,700
I will treat her well with all my heart.

427
00:23:25,460 --> 00:23:27,350
I don't need acknowledgement.

428
00:23:27,770 --> 00:23:29,660
This is what I have always wanted to do.

429
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:31,170
Do you understand?

430
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:34,000
I get it.

431
00:23:37,220 --> 00:23:38,070
Wu Zhi Xun.

432
00:23:38,070 --> 00:23:39,830
You have changed my view about you.

433
00:23:43,390 --> 00:23:44,060
Let's go.

434
00:23:53,890 --> 00:23:55,700
Thanks for walking us back.

435
00:23:58,980 --> 00:23:59,900
Be happy.

436
00:23:59,900 --> 00:24:00,620
I'll go off now.

437
00:24:01,030 --> 00:24:01,660
Bye.

438
00:24:09,230 --> 00:24:10,610
Are you satisfied now?

439
00:24:11,450 --> 00:24:11,990
Let's go in.

440
00:24:13,340 --> 00:24:14,940
Bring this back for me.

441
00:24:14,940 --> 00:24:15,980
I have something to do.

442
00:24:16,660 --> 00:24:17,500
Wait, where are you going?

443
00:24:18,210 --> 00:24:19,260
Don't mind me.

444
00:24:19,260 --> 00:24:20,350
I want to take a walk.

445
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:31,400
We have been classmates for so many years.

446
00:24:31,900 --> 00:24:33,670
But I think I didn't really know you.

447
00:24:34,670 --> 00:24:36,190
We really didn't know about each other.

448
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:40,760
Actually,

449
00:24:41,110 --> 00:24:42,910
I'm still a little worried.

450
00:24:44,560 --> 00:24:45,190
Why?

451
00:24:46,150 --> 00:24:47,630
I'm different from you.

452
00:24:48,550 --> 00:24:50,480
I'm not as easy going as you.

453
00:24:50,980 --> 00:24:51,830
Li Qing Tong...

454
00:24:51,830 --> 00:24:53,680
She is also a very stubborn person.

455
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:55,230
After some time,

456
00:24:55,520 --> 00:24:57,150
there will definitely be many problems.

457
00:24:57,910 --> 00:24:59,800
We have to be apart for several years.

458
00:25:00,480 --> 00:25:02,750
I'm afraid that there
will be more problems.

459
00:25:02,750 --> 00:25:03,870
It's not that serious.

460
00:25:04,260 --> 00:25:05,390
People will change.

461
00:25:05,730 --> 00:25:08,250
Li Qing Tong is a different person
when she is with you.

462
00:25:08,250 --> 00:25:09,300
She's obedient

463
00:25:09,300 --> 00:25:10,100
and patient.

464
00:25:11,010 --> 00:25:12,230
Didn't you change a lot too?

465
00:25:12,660 --> 00:25:13,660
You make her happy

466
00:25:14,130 --> 00:25:15,350
and you compromise.

467
00:25:15,350 --> 00:25:16,270
It's good, right?

468
00:25:17,110 --> 00:25:18,710
No matter how far apart you are,

469
00:25:19,550 --> 00:25:21,350
as long as you are determined,

470
00:25:21,820 --> 00:25:22,900
everything will be okay.

471
00:25:23,290 --> 00:25:25,010
I hope so.

472
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:31,220
Hello.

473
00:25:36,150 --> 00:25:36,910
You go home first.

474
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:37,950
I have to go back again.

475
00:25:38,710 --> 00:25:39,340
Bye.

476
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:55,630
What are you doing?

477
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:56,850
Did you miss me?

478
00:25:57,360 --> 00:25:58,530
Why are you here?

479
00:25:58,530 --> 00:25:59,670
I want to ask you that.

480
00:25:59,670 --> 00:26:00,970
Why are you sitting here alone?

481
00:26:05,210 --> 00:26:06,180
What's up?

482
00:26:07,350 --> 00:26:09,380
Do you also think that

483
00:26:10,130 --> 00:26:12,050
I am too sentimental,

484
00:26:12,600 --> 00:26:14,210
and always create trouble?

485
00:26:15,540 --> 00:26:16,340
Why?

486
00:26:19,190 --> 00:26:20,710
Just like how it is now.

487
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:24,070
Everyone thinks everything is good.

488
00:26:24,610 --> 00:26:27,640
Only I feel depressed and sad
without any reason,

489
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:29,440
and make other people unhappy.

490
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,960
Am I annoying?

491
00:26:33,180 --> 00:26:34,520
A little bit.

492
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:37,880
But I can understand you.

493
00:26:44,100 --> 00:26:45,240
Actually,

494
00:26:46,340 --> 00:26:48,340
I feel sorry for Chen Jun He.

495
00:26:49,690 --> 00:26:50,440
Why?

496
00:26:52,790 --> 00:26:54,150
If it weren't for me,

497
00:26:54,690 --> 00:26:57,080
he would not have so many
conflicts with Li Qing Tong.

498
00:26:58,250 --> 00:27:00,740
After all, their conflicts
are caused by me.

499
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:02,510
Besides,

500
00:27:03,180 --> 00:27:04,940
it was me

501
00:27:04,940 --> 00:27:07,910
who pushed Wu Zhi Xun
to Li Qing Tong.

502
00:27:08,380 --> 00:27:09,980
If it weren't for me,

503
00:27:09,980 --> 00:27:12,420
the one having a relationship
with Li Qing Tong now

504
00:27:12,420 --> 00:27:13,670
is probably Chen Jun He.

505
00:27:14,210 --> 00:27:15,890
What if it was Chen Junhe now?

506
00:27:18,080 --> 00:27:19,170
Whether it is Chen Junhe

507
00:27:19,630 --> 00:27:20,600
or Wu Zhi Xun,

508
00:27:20,990 --> 00:27:22,990
it's all up to Li Qing Tong.

509
00:27:23,370 --> 00:27:24,760
It's none of our business.

510
00:27:27,110 --> 00:27:28,590
You told me before that

511
00:27:29,220 --> 00:27:30,720
you are a person who pursues freedom.

512
00:27:30,980 --> 00:27:32,060
I support you.

513
00:27:33,420 --> 00:27:36,310
Everyone's life should be free.

514
00:27:36,820 --> 00:27:40,760
We shouldn't force others to change.

515
00:27:42,730 --> 00:27:44,120
Because we have no rights.

516
00:27:46,940 --> 00:27:48,110
As a good friend,

517
00:27:48,740 --> 00:27:50,130
we can support each other,

518
00:27:50,500 --> 00:27:51,970
but we can't control each other.

519
00:27:53,900 --> 00:27:55,550
So, if you really want to help her,

520
00:27:56,130 --> 00:27:59,110
you should help Li Qing Tong
be what she wants to be,

521
00:27:59,110 --> 00:28:00,720
instead of forcing her

522
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:01,970
to be what you want her to be.

523
00:28:01,970 --> 00:28:02,900
Is that right?

524
00:28:03,360 --> 00:28:04,280
I didn't know

525
00:28:04,820 --> 00:28:06,300
you can say something so sensible.

526
00:28:06,300 --> 00:28:07,650
Oh my gosh!

527
00:28:07,650 --> 00:28:09,320
I know a lot of truths.

528
00:28:10,240 --> 00:28:12,170
I know you are right.

529
00:28:12,170 --> 00:28:14,060
I also know what you said makes sense.

530
00:28:14,450 --> 00:28:15,150
But...

531
00:28:33,810 --> 00:28:35,240
But...

532
00:28:44,550 --> 00:28:45,440
What?

533
00:29:01,940 --> 00:29:02,780
Hua, what's wrong with you?

534
00:29:02,780 --> 00:29:04,460
You didn't come back last night?

535
00:29:04,460 --> 00:29:05,890
Did you lie down for a day?

536
00:29:05,890 --> 00:29:07,030
Are you hungry?

537
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:09,630
Are you sick?

538
00:29:12,780 --> 00:29:13,450
Well, what's wrong with you?

539
00:29:13,450 --> 00:29:14,670
Don't scare me.

540
00:29:18,070 --> 00:29:18,950
I am hungry.

541
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:28,860
Can you finish all these food?

542
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:31,170
I don't think these are enough.

543
00:29:31,690 --> 00:29:32,850
I'll order more food for you.

544
00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:33,910
Let's go.

545
00:29:37,100 --> 00:29:38,440
Well, what's wrong?

546
00:29:39,870 --> 00:29:40,590
Li Qing Tong.

547
00:29:41,170 --> 00:29:42,690
I have made a decision.

548
00:29:43,190 --> 00:29:45,580
I will only be responsible
for my own affairs,

549
00:29:45,580 --> 00:29:46,460
and will not care about you anymore.

550
00:29:47,050 --> 00:29:48,560
What do you mean?

551
00:29:49,280 --> 00:29:50,710
I mean

552
00:29:50,710 --> 00:29:53,220
I won't force you to do
what you don't want to do.

553
00:29:53,770 --> 00:29:55,410
The situation now is all caused by me.

554
00:29:55,410 --> 00:29:56,830
It has nothing to do with you.

555
00:29:56,830 --> 00:29:59,320
I shouldn't force you into
liking or disliking anyone.

556
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:01,170
I have no rights.

557
00:30:05,650 --> 00:30:06,830
After all these years,

558
00:30:07,220 --> 00:30:08,510
have I had one day

559
00:30:08,510 --> 00:30:10,440
that I want, Li Jin Bu?

560
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:12,090
Now I am a scourge to you, right?

561
00:30:13,180 --> 00:30:14,640
What I want is just a childhood

562
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:16,160
that is not so vagrant,

563
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:17,130
a caring mom

564
00:30:17,130 --> 00:30:18,220
and a dad who doesn't run away.

565
00:30:18,220 --> 00:30:19,140
Am I not worthy?

566
00:30:19,140 --> 00:30:20,560
I am not worthy.

567
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:22,420
I am the one who is not worthy, okay?

568
00:30:23,850 --> 00:30:25,560
From the moment I gave birth to you,

569
00:30:25,560 --> 00:30:28,890
I am not worthy to have a stable life.

570
00:30:30,990 --> 00:30:31,540
In future,

571
00:30:31,540 --> 00:30:34,060
you can have a life that you want.

572
00:30:34,800 --> 00:30:36,280
You can be with whoever you like.

573
00:30:36,280 --> 00:30:37,250
You can get married if you want.

574
00:30:37,250 --> 00:30:38,750
It doesn't matter whether
you want to have a baby or not.

575
00:30:40,020 --> 00:30:41,140
You always say that

576
00:30:41,140 --> 00:30:43,240
you have never had a life that you want.

577
00:30:43,760 --> 00:30:45,090
Now, you can restart.

578
00:30:45,520 --> 00:30:47,370
I will be responsible for my decision.

579
00:30:48,280 --> 00:30:48,960
Well, are you confused

580
00:30:48,960 --> 00:30:50,510
because of the soup?

581
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:51,730
Don't scare me.

582
00:30:52,330 --> 00:30:54,580
Anyway, you can continue to be
in love with Wu Zhi Xun.

583
00:30:54,580 --> 00:30:55,640
I give you my best wishes.

584
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:57,360
But if he bullies you, just tell me.

585
00:30:57,360 --> 00:30:58,240
I will help you.

586
00:31:01,980 --> 00:31:02,400
Jin Bu.

587
00:31:02,980 --> 00:31:03,360
Here you go.

588
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:06,890
It seems that

589
00:31:06,890 --> 00:31:08,020
it's good to eat more.

590
00:31:08,020 --> 00:31:09,790
It makes you more sensible.

591
00:31:09,790 --> 00:31:10,510
I also want to eat.

592
00:31:10,510 --> 00:31:10,930
Share it with me.

593
00:31:10,930 --> 00:31:12,100
I want to eat it too.

594
00:31:12,100 --> 00:31:12,490
Give it to me.

595
00:31:12,490 --> 00:31:12,910
I want to eat.

596
00:31:13,700 --> 00:31:14,910
I ordered this.

597
00:31:14,910 --> 00:31:16,640
Can't I have a bite?

598
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:17,390
Stop fighting over it.

599
00:31:17,390 --> 00:31:18,270
What's wrong with you?

600
00:31:18,270 --> 00:31:19,960
You go to fetch
another pair of chopsticks.

601
00:31:34,270 --> 00:31:35,320
Hello, Professor He.

602
00:31:39,940 --> 00:31:40,630
I got it.

603
00:31:41,090 --> 00:31:42,000
Thank you, Professor He.

604
00:31:56,530 --> 00:31:56,580
Congratulations to your kid for
being admitted into an ideal university.

605
00:31:56,580 --> 00:31:58,490
[Congratulations to our student Wu Zhi Xun
for entering Tsin Ku University]

606
00:31:58,490 --> 00:31:59,770
Thank you for everything.

607
00:31:59,810 --> 00:32:00,620
Not at all.

608
00:32:00,660 --> 00:32:02,720
This is the result of everyone's effort.

609
00:32:02,830 --> 00:32:04,610
We really owe it to the school.

610
00:32:04,610 --> 00:32:05,440
Not at all.

611
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:06,530
I need to go now.

612
00:32:07,120 --> 00:32:07,710
Bye.

613
00:32:08,630 --> 00:32:09,930
Thank you for your concern.

614
00:32:09,930 --> 00:32:10,810
Thank you.

615
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:12,330
Well done.

616
00:32:12,790 --> 00:32:14,000
I'm proud of you.

617
00:32:17,410 --> 00:32:18,500
It's okay.

618
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:18,550
[Lin Yang Teachers College]

619
00:32:18,550 --> 00:32:20,670
It's great that he is
going to university now.

620
00:32:35,890 --> 00:32:38,290
Actually, they look good together.

621
00:32:38,290 --> 00:32:41,300
They are willing to help each other grow.

622
00:32:45,680 --> 00:32:46,560
That's good!

623
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:48,410
We are the same too.

624
00:32:48,410 --> 00:32:49,700
I become a fool for you.

625
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:50,960
And you become a fool for me.

626
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:51,970
Perfect!

627
00:33:07,300 --> 00:33:08,350
Dad.

628
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:09,360
Mom.

629
00:33:12,890 --> 00:33:15,040
What's wrong? Nobody is home.

630
00:33:15,830 --> 00:33:17,170
How long were they gone?

631
00:33:18,110 --> 00:33:19,400
They have forgotten their daughter.

632
00:33:22,590 --> 00:33:23,940
Why are you home?

633
00:33:28,560 --> 00:33:29,320
I forgot about it.

634
00:33:31,160 --> 00:33:32,300
You are on holiday?

635
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:34,100
How could you even ask?

636
00:33:34,520 --> 00:33:35,960
You said you would pick us up.

637
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:36,620
Not only did you not come to pick us up,

638
00:33:36,620 --> 00:33:38,510
but you also forgot the date.

639
00:33:39,360 --> 00:33:41,000
We are just busy.

640
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:42,160
Don't be angry.

641
00:33:42,160 --> 00:33:43,130
Where is my dad?

642
00:33:44,350 --> 00:33:44,860
Well.

643
00:33:45,770 --> 00:33:46,620
Working overtime.

644
00:33:46,620 --> 00:33:47,590
He is working overtime.

645
00:33:48,630 --> 00:33:49,480
Working overtime again?

646
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:51,820
Why does he always work overtime?

647
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:54,130
Only by working overtime
can he get a high paid.

648
00:33:54,770 --> 00:33:56,440
You didn't have lunch, right?

649
00:33:56,440 --> 00:33:57,870
I'm going to prepare
something delicious for you.

650
00:33:57,870 --> 00:33:59,760
It'll be ready soon.

651
00:34:02,950 --> 00:34:05,010
Why do I feel that she's a little haggard?

652
00:34:05,010 --> 00:34:06,270
Really?

653
00:34:06,270 --> 00:34:08,030
You are not a keen observer.

654
00:34:08,909 --> 00:34:10,429
Auntie, I'll help you.

655
00:34:25,139 --> 00:34:26,719
[Daily Neccessity Supermarket
and Restaurant]

656
00:34:26,980 --> 00:34:28,080
Really?

657
00:34:29,290 --> 00:34:31,800
Of course. I even received a love letter.

658
00:34:33,190 --> 00:34:34,620
There is really someone
who dares take the challenge.

659
00:34:35,340 --> 00:34:36,350
What are you saying?

660
00:34:37,600 --> 00:34:38,360
That's good!

661
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:39,489
I'm relieved now.

662
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,760
But, Tong.

663
00:34:40,969 --> 00:34:42,560
I'm worried about you.

664
00:34:42,560 --> 00:34:44,949
I'm afraid that you will be bullied
when you are with Wu Zhixun.

665
00:34:45,380 --> 00:34:46,560
He is not how he used to be.

666
00:34:46,560 --> 00:34:47,719
He is good now.

667
00:34:47,719 --> 00:34:48,870
Really?

668
00:34:48,870 --> 00:34:50,659
Then you call him and let me have a look.

669
00:34:50,659 --> 00:34:52,550
If I disagree with the relationship,

670
00:34:52,550 --> 00:34:53,520
he will be out.

671
00:34:54,650 --> 00:34:55,920
He has gone back to his hometown.

672
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,720
I'll show him to you when he is free.

673
00:34:58,140 --> 00:34:58,780
Fine.

674
00:34:59,690 --> 00:35:00,570
How about Ba Dan?

675
00:35:00,570 --> 00:35:01,710
It feels like we haven't
contacted for a long time.

676
00:35:01,710 --> 00:35:02,550
Yes.

677
00:35:03,350 --> 00:35:04,950
I forgot to tell you.

678
00:35:04,950 --> 00:35:07,760
Ba Dan seems to be a totally different
person after entering university.

679
00:35:08,050 --> 00:35:09,480
He pursues different girls every day.

680
00:35:09,480 --> 00:35:11,340
He confesses his love and
sends girls flowers every day.

681
00:35:11,340 --> 00:35:12,880
But nobody cares about him.

682
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:14,010
Is that true?

683
00:35:20,400 --> 00:35:21,150
Look.

684
00:35:21,670 --> 00:35:24,100
Who did you go after today?

685
00:35:25,350 --> 00:35:25,770
Well.

686
00:35:26,290 --> 00:35:27,450
You failed?

687
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:29,760
What's up?

688
00:35:32,030 --> 00:35:33,040
What's the big deal?

689
00:35:33,040 --> 00:35:34,340
Stop treating it so serious.

690
00:35:34,800 --> 00:35:36,620
You still have us.

691
00:35:36,990 --> 00:35:38,300
What does she think she is?

692
00:35:38,300 --> 00:35:39,300
I will introduce one to you.

693
00:35:39,550 --> 00:35:40,220
There are plenty of girls

694
00:35:40,220 --> 00:35:41,270
in my university.

695
00:35:41,270 --> 00:35:42,150
Okay?

696
00:35:42,150 --> 00:35:43,000
Let's enjoy the meal.

697
00:35:45,310 --> 00:35:46,410
No, thanks.

698
00:35:47,540 --> 00:35:49,670
I can see it now.

699
00:35:50,300 --> 00:35:51,730
Those girls

700
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:54,500
only love my money

701
00:35:54,500 --> 00:35:57,410
instead of my talents.

702
00:36:03,990 --> 00:36:05,630
They are not as good as you, Li Qing Tong.

703
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:10,180
I will give these flowers to you.

704
00:36:11,940 --> 00:36:12,900
Take it.

705
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:15,290
Buddy.

706
00:36:15,290 --> 00:36:17,520
Flowers can't be given to anyone randomly.

707
00:36:17,990 --> 00:36:18,690
You can't give them to Li Qingtong.

708
00:36:18,690 --> 00:36:19,670
Nobody wants you.

709
00:36:19,670 --> 00:36:20,250
But someone wants her.

710
00:36:20,250 --> 00:36:21,180
Wu Zhi Xun wants her.

711
00:36:21,180 --> 00:36:22,890
If Wu Zhi Xun finds the flowers,

712
00:36:22,890 --> 00:36:24,190
he will slap you with a book.

713
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:24,990
Take back your flowers.

714
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,350
Slap me?

715
00:36:28,270 --> 00:36:29,870
Why do you mention Wu Zhi Xun?

716
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:32,930
He has only been with Li Qing Tong
for several days.

717
00:36:34,740 --> 00:36:36,720
I have known Li Qing Tong
for more than 20 years.

718
00:36:37,510 --> 00:36:39,910
From kindergarten to this day.

719
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:42,100
How long have they known each other?

720
00:36:42,100 --> 00:36:44,070
Wu Zhi Xun? Chen Jun He?

721
00:36:44,070 --> 00:36:45,990
Do they treat Li Qing Tong well?

722
00:36:49,180 --> 00:36:50,740
I am going to like you today.

723
00:36:51,880 --> 00:36:52,500
Take this.

724
00:36:54,600 --> 00:36:55,960
Well, buddy.

725
00:36:56,580 --> 00:36:57,930
We have not seen each other
for a long time.

726
00:36:57,930 --> 00:36:58,690
Let's have a chat.

727
00:36:58,690 --> 00:36:59,850
Let's go somewhere else for a drink.

728
00:37:00,150 --> 00:37:00,520
Well, let's go.

729
00:37:00,520 --> 00:37:01,120
Do you think I am drunk?

730
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:01,620
Let's have a drink.

731
00:37:01,740 --> 00:37:03,300
I like Li Qing Tong.
What is wrong with that?

732
00:37:04,680 --> 00:37:06,290
I also like Fan Shui Shui.

733
00:37:06,990 --> 00:37:08,670
Half of the flowers is for Fan Shui Shui.

734
00:37:09,270 --> 00:37:10,180
I really...

735
00:37:23,750 --> 00:37:24,970
How embarrassing!

736
00:37:29,850 --> 00:37:31,310
What did I do?

737
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:33,590
How can I face them in future?

738
00:37:34,010 --> 00:37:34,810
It's okay.

739
00:37:34,810 --> 00:37:36,180
What is done is done.

740
00:37:36,180 --> 00:37:37,540
It is useless to think about it now.

741
00:37:38,030 --> 00:37:38,540
Come on.

742
00:37:38,910 --> 00:37:39,710
Let's have a drink.

743
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:41,890
What?

744
00:37:42,100 --> 00:37:43,200
Have a drink.

745
00:37:43,740 --> 00:37:44,540
Again?

746
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:46,690
If I didn't drink,

747
00:37:46,690 --> 00:37:48,070
I won't regret it so much now.

748
00:37:53,990 --> 00:37:55,000
Today,

749
00:37:55,630 --> 00:37:56,640
was I embarrassing?

750
00:37:57,020 --> 00:37:57,640
No.

751
00:37:58,030 --> 00:37:59,000
You are same as usual.

752
00:37:59,950 --> 00:38:01,040
Is that what I usually do?

753
00:38:05,540 --> 00:38:07,350
That's how decadent I am usually.

754
00:38:12,930 --> 00:38:13,860
Where are you going?

755
00:38:14,750 --> 00:38:16,000
I got to go if you don't want a drink.

756
00:38:16,750 --> 00:38:17,340
What?

757
00:38:17,340 --> 00:38:18,770
You call yourself a friend?

758
00:38:20,580 --> 00:38:21,160
No, wait.

759
00:38:25,200 --> 00:38:26,300
Don't drink too much.

760
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:27,050
Hurry up now.

761
00:38:28,010 --> 00:38:29,390
What a mess!

762
00:38:42,470 --> 00:38:44,100
Why are you drinking alone?

763
00:38:44,440 --> 00:38:45,480
Why are you here?

764
00:38:46,410 --> 00:38:47,330
Ask him.

765
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:48,760
What happened?

766
00:38:50,700 --> 00:38:51,710
What's the matter?

767
00:38:57,450 --> 00:38:59,260
I confessed to Li Qing Tong.

768
00:38:59,970 --> 00:39:00,640
What?

769
00:39:03,260 --> 00:39:03,830
I said

770
00:39:04,420 --> 00:39:06,240
I confessed to Li Qing Tong.

771
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:07,570
I was drunk.

772
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:09,880
You are courageous, buddy.

773
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:10,940
A toast to you.

774
00:39:18,370 --> 00:39:20,590
Only Xiao have a successful outcome here.

775
00:39:21,190 --> 00:39:22,740
Jack shall have Jill.

776
00:39:23,110 --> 00:39:24,330
What's the matter with us?

777
00:39:25,810 --> 00:39:27,450
Because God helps those
who help themselves.

778
00:39:27,450 --> 00:39:28,400
Do you understand?

779
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:30,130
You have to reflect on yourselves.

780
00:39:30,130 --> 00:39:30,920
One is stubborn.

781
00:39:30,920 --> 00:39:31,650
The other is decadent.

782
00:39:31,650 --> 00:39:32,610
Who could you blame?

783
00:39:34,170 --> 00:39:35,120
If I knew I would end up like that,

784
00:39:35,500 --> 00:39:37,060
I should have confess my love
to Fan Shui Shui just now.

785
00:39:42,650 --> 00:39:44,450
Did I confess to Fan Shui Shui just now?

786
00:39:45,170 --> 00:39:46,050
That's a good thing.

787
00:39:46,050 --> 00:39:47,640
I actually think you are
suitable for each other.

788
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,700
Doomed love.

789
00:39:58,060 --> 00:39:58,560
Cheers!

790
00:39:58,560 --> 00:39:59,270
Refill it.

791
00:40:00,670 --> 00:40:02,130
What a mess!

792
00:40:05,660 --> 00:40:08,510
Ba Dan just disappeared
after he went to the bathroom.

793
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,420
What's your plan?

794
00:40:12,890 --> 00:40:14,110
You are cutting ties with us?

795
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:16,750
I will let nature take its course.

796
00:40:17,420 --> 00:40:19,150
It doesn't affect you guys anyway.

797
00:40:19,520 --> 00:40:20,830
As for Li Qing Tong,

798
00:40:21,160 --> 00:40:22,500
she doesn't need me.

799
00:40:22,890 --> 00:40:24,900
After all, Jack shall have Jill.

800
00:40:24,900 --> 00:40:26,820
It's not suitable for me to appear again.

801
00:40:28,970 --> 00:40:30,950
It's nothing. No big deal.

802
00:40:34,050 --> 00:40:34,690
What are you doing?

803
00:40:34,690 --> 00:40:36,020
What are you talking about?

804
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:37,450
Well.

805
00:40:37,950 --> 00:40:38,670
Let's go for another round.

806
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:40,610
Let's drink some more.
Call Li Qing Tong out.

807
00:40:58,330 --> 00:41:00,170
I heard that you have a good time here

808
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:02,310
and also have a boyfriend.

809
00:41:03,110 --> 00:41:04,290
Too bad.

810
00:41:04,510 --> 00:41:06,390
You have to go back.

811
00:41:13,780 --> 00:41:14,710
Take it easy.

812
00:41:15,180 --> 00:41:16,600
It's not now.

813
00:41:16,940 --> 00:41:18,450
How long can I stay here?

814
00:41:19,250 --> 00:41:21,260
I can't tell you the exact date.

815
00:41:23,570 --> 00:41:25,170
Just cherish every day here.
